> It is possible to use RSA in your software ...
> but commercial use is impossible

Except with a license. And licenses are available. (I'm talking about
RSAREF, and assume the poster was as well.)

> Also exporting it out of the USA is not allowed.

Unless:

- your customer overseas is a bank or US company.  
- your use is authentication only (no restrictions at all).  
- you simply apply for and receive an export license. Trading
  speed for security may very well get you export approval.


     
